    <section id="biology">
        <h2>Biology</h2>
        <p>Biology is the study of life. From the cells in our bodies to the ecosystems that span the globe, biology helps us understand living organisms and how they interact with their environment.</p>
    </section>

    <section id="physics">
        <h2>Physics</h2>
        <p>Physics explores the fundamental forces of the universe, from gravity to electromagnetism. It helps us understand how the world works, from the motion of planets to the behavior of subatomic particles.</p>
    </section>

    <section id="chemistry">
        <h2>Chemistry</h2>
        <p>Chemistry is the study of matter and its interactions. It explains everything from the food we eat to the materials we use, and even the reactions happening in stars far away.</p>
    </section>

